WEBVTT

2
00:00:22.017 --> 00:00:23.096
Nau mai ki te tēpu.

3
00:00:23.096 --> 00:00:30.046
Ko te whakakotahitanga o te arawa hei whakahaere i ōna painga te kaupapa

4
00:00:30.046 --> 00:00:34.021
kei konei te kīnaki o ngā kōrero.

5
00:00:34.021 --> 00:00:34.099
Kēti.

6
00:00:34.099 --> 00:00:41.046
Kia kōrero pono au ki a koe Chris, he mahi nui māku i tēnei wā,

7
00:00:41.046 --> 00:00:46.066
he whakakotahi i a Ngāti Rangitihi, ko tētahi o ngā iwi o roto i a Te Arawa.

8
00:00:46.066 --> 00:00:54.014
Heoi anō, tino tautoko ahau i te whakakotahitanga

9
00:00:54.014 --> 00:00:57.080
mā reira e tū rangatira ai a Te Arawa.

10
00:00:57.080 --> 00:01:03.038
i runga i tōna te arawatanga hei hāpai i ōna iwi

11
00:01:03.038 --> 00:01:09.012
Kia whai oranga te katoa i runga i te tū kotahi nei

12
00:01:09.012 --> 00:01:11.066
Tēnā koe. Toby.

13
00:01:11.066 --> 00:01:22.042
Ki tāku ko te mea nui, kaua kē waiho mā te ture Pākehā hei whakamana i a tātou.

14
00:01:22.042 --> 00:01:28.053
Engari waiho mā wā mātou, well, mā wā tātou tikanga,

15
00:01:28.053 --> 00:01:32.063
wā tātou mātauranga,

16
00:01:32.063 --> 00:01:40.012
wā tātou huarahi i waihotia nei e kui mā, e koro mā,

17
00:01:40.012 --> 00:01:44.030
hei whakamana i wā tātou mahi.

18
00:01:44.030 --> 00:01:49.006
Te kauhanga nui tōna kanohi o mua mamae,

19
00:01:49.006 --> 00:01:54.088
kei te mihi atu ki ngā kōrero o Toby rāua ko Kathy, kia kaha ki a au, kia manawanui.

20
00:01:54.088 --> 00:01:58.081
Kōkiringia atu i roto i ngā taonga i tuku iho mai e rātou,

21
00:01:58.081 --> 00:02:01.061
ka eke, ka eke te tao.

22
00:02:01.061 --> 00:02:03.045
Tēnā rā koe.

23
00:02:03.045 --> 00:02:10.060
He kōrero kāore i whai wā ki te kōrero i runga i tā tātou kaupapa nei ka timata mai i a koe Kathy,

24
00:02:10.060 --> 00:02:16.022
He mahuetanga kōrero e toe ana.

25
00:02:16.022 --> 00:02:29.061
Ki aku whakaaro kua kōrerotia aku take katoa i te rangi nei, engari pīrangi au ki te kauhau anō mō te reo,

26
00:02:29.061 --> 00:02:34.038
me taku whakapono kei roto i te reo te rongoā,

27
00:02:34.038 --> 00:02:43.029
ka whakakotahingia a Te Arawa, mēnā ko te reo me ngā tikanga kei te ārahi i a mātou.

28
00:02:43.029 --> 00:02:44.089
Tēnā koe.

29
00:02:44.089 --> 00:02:49.051
Toby, he mahuetanga kōrero, āe,

30
00:02:49.051 --> 00:02:58.025
ko te... tētahi whakaaro tūturu i roto i tēnei me te maru o te arawa,

31
00:02:58.025 --> 00:03:03.037
mehemea ka taea mātou te... te whakatū i tērā āhuatanga

32
00:03:03.037 --> 00:03:11.002
kia tuku atu te mana ki wētahi o mātou tāngata

33
00:03:11.002 --> 00:03:17.030
kāore koe e kite rātou i runga i te paepae, engari tino kakama, tino pakari.

34
00:03:17.030 --> 00:03:28.027
me te tuku hoki rā te mana ki wā tātou wāhine hei kōrero mō te aro i runga i wētahi o ngā āhuatanga e pā ana ki a mātou.

35
00:03:28.027 --> 00:03:41.062
Anā, ngā mahi pākihi, mahi hauora, ngā mahi e pā ana ki ngā wāhine, mā te wāhine anō e kōrero mō ngā wāhine o te aro,

36
00:03:41.062 --> 00:03:47.049
Kaua kē waiho mā te tāne hei kōrero i ngā... i ngā take mō ngā wāhine.

37
00:03:47.049 --> 00:03:49.070
Koinei noa iho kei... kei a au i tēnei wā.

38
00:03:49.070 --> 00:03:52.045
Mōmai he pātai tāku,

39
00:03:52.045 --> 00:03:57.053
ehara i te pātai engari kia tangohia ngā kōrero nei mai i te Kīngitanga,

40
00:03:57.053 --> 00:04:00.038
Turakina ngā taiapa ki raro.

41
00:04:00.038 --> 00:04:04.015
Kia uru mai a waho ki roto, kia ū, kia mau,

42
00:04:04.015 --> 00:04:08.063
kei tāngorongoro ka ngā whewhe.

43
00:04:08.063 --> 00:04:10.085
Tēnā rā koutou kei aku rangatira.

44
00:04:10.085 --> 00:04:20.014
Kāti waiho pērā, koinā ngā kōrero maunu e hī ai te ika.

45
00:04:20.014 --> 00:04:21.059
Tēnā koutou katoa.

46
00:04:21.059 --> 00:04:28.081
Ko te tēpu, mātaki mai.
